rComments: She was an incredibily hard marker. It was an interesting class. She posted her powerpoints online but always took attendance.

I thought prof. haase was amazing.  her course was interesting and she was an amazing accent, which i honestly love in a professor. The course is pretty hard i wont lie but prof. haase is very good. also i found her accent helped me stay focused a lot of the time, because it is such an interesting one.

Definitely not easy to understand what she's saying, especially when she's giving Greek or Roman names, maybe if she wrote them on the board it would be better. Her lectures are quite boring, all she does is read her ppt lecture. Shes a really nice lady though. lol
2 midterms, 10% participation marks, 1 final worth 40%  overall: a course worth taking!
